Package Library

Class Library

java.lang.Object
Library.Library
public class Library
extends java.lang.Object
Library class representing catalog of Book objects. Store books in multiples of 4.
Author:
Connie Chen, Tiffany Lee

    • quickSort

      public void quickSort​(Book[] books, int low, int high, boolean sortType)
      Quick sort method that sorts the Book in Library in ascending order. Divide and conquer method for the array of Books.
      Parameters:
      books - the bag of Books to be sorted
      low - the beginning index of the array to be sorted
      high - the end index of the array to be sorted
      sortType - sorting either by Date or by serial number
